  <center><h1>Preserved Tapa Meat</h1><hr style="height:5px;border-width:0;color:gray;background-color:#9A3A18">
<p> Tapa is a Filipino cuisine made out of thinly sliced beef or pork. Tapa is commonly marinated in a sweet, salty, and tangy marinade made with calamansi lemonade and soy sauce, flavored with sugar and minced garlic which will give the Tapa an appetizing flavor. </p></center>
<hr style="height:3px;border-width:0;color:gray;background-color:#9A3A18">

