     <p3>  Insert Formula: 648.6 * 0.2 = 129.72</p3><br>


<p3>Multiply the total cost per portion to 20% (0.2 in decimal form)</p3><br><br>


<p3> <b>E. Selling Price = Php 778.32</b> </p3><br>

<p3>Insert Formula: 648.6 + 129.72 = 778.32 </p3><br>

